PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the use by the PROVINCE OF ALBERTA of its statutory power to acquire several pieces of land on Wabasca Indian Reserve No. 166, for the purposes of Highway 813, and (b) in lieu thereof, transferring the lands to the Province for so long as they are used for those purposes.

precis:
Order (a) consenting to the use by the PROVINCE OF ALBERTA of its statutory
power to acquire several pieces of land on Wabasca Indian Reserve No. 166,
for the purposes of Highway 813, and (b) in lieu thereof, transferring the
